title: Renegade 3 in. Classic Trench Shovel with 48 in. Ash Wood Handle
description: After 35 years, Hisco's mission continues to focus on providing our customers the highest quality professional grade hand tools. The Renegade 3 in. Classic Trench Shovel is a strong and sturdy tool that features a 48 in. handle. The blade is extremely tough and can withstand many years of use on the farm or jobsite.
